les ballets trockadero de monte carlo.data-term: les ballets trockadero de monte carlo

examples.en: We are getting to the pointy end of this speech.
She has short blond curly hair, purple eyes, and pointy ears.
You must put the cutlery in the dishwasher pointy end up, not down.
She was wearing a pointy hat.
Don't try to argue when you find yourself at the pointy end of a knife.
She was described to have a pointy chin, an upturned nose and wore a long flowing robe.
